###`create user`

```curl --location --request POST 'http://core.localhost/api/app/register' \
   --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \

       "password":123456789,
       "confirm":123456789,
       "first_name":"nghia",
       "last_name":"tran",
       "avatar":"data:image/png;base64,",

   }

```

####`login user`
`curl example`
```
curl --location --request POST 'http://core.localhost/api/app/login' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
    "email":"tranvannghia021@gmail.com",

}'
```

### `get info`
```
curl --location --request GET 'http://core.localhost/api/app/info' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer {{token}}'
```
### `update info`

```
curl --location --request POST 'http://core.localhost/api/app/info' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer {{token}}' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
    "first_name":"ng"
}'
```
### `change-password`
```
curl --location --request PUT 'http://core.localhost/api/app/change-password' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer {{token}}' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
    "password_old":123456789,
    "password":12345678
}'
```

### `delete`

```
curl --location --request DELETE 'http://core.localhost/api/app/delete' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer {{token}}'
```
